[
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-11-10T16:05:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467af",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T08:30:00+00:00",
    "order": "0",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Park County school consolidation fight. Case studies, vote count, talking points, op-ed. Everything for the board lives here.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-11-10T16:05:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467b0",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T08:30:00+00:00",
    "order": "1",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Quick links",
    "type": "heading_2"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-11-10T16:05:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467b1",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T08:30:00+00:00",
    "order": "2",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Case studies — four Wyoming counties that already consolidated.",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-11-22T19:40:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467b9",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-01T15:20:00+00:00",
    "order": "0",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "text": "Niobrara County. Closed the Lusk-area elementary back in 2014. Smallest district in the state — worth a hard look.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-11-22T19:40:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467ba",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-01T15:20:00+00:00",
    "order": "1",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "text": "What happened",
    "type": "heading_2"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-11-22T19:40:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467bb",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-01T15:20:00+00:00",
    "order": "2",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "text": "Bus runs stretched past an hour each way after the closure. Enrollment kept dropping anyway.",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-11-22T19:40:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467bc",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-01T15:20:00+00:00",
    "order": "3",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "text": "Pull Niobrara enrollment 2012–2020 from the WDE site.",
    "type": "to_do"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-12-05T14:15:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467c3",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-03-18T11:05:00+00:00",
    "order": "0",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "text": "Hot Springs County, Thermopolis. Folded two rural elementaries into town. Bus times went on record.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-12-05T14:15:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467c4",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-03-18T11:05:00+00:00",
    "order": "1",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "text": "Findings",
    "type": "heading_2"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-12-05T14:15:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467c5",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-03-18T11:05:00+00:00",
    "order": "2",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "text": "Outlying families saw rides grow to 45–50 minutes. Same number we're staring at for Sage Creek.",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-12-05T14:15:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467c6",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-03-18T11:05:00+00:00",
    "order": "3",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "text": "Get route mileage from the Hot Springs Co. transportation office.",
    "type": "to_do"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-12-18T21:30:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467cd",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-02-12T09:45:00+00:00",
    "order": "0",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "text": "Washakie County, Worland. Tried consolidation, reversed it within two years. Numbers didn't pencil out.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-12-18T21:30:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467ce",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-02-12T09:45:00+00:00",
    "order": "1",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "text": "Why it failed",
    "type": "heading_2"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-12-18T21:30:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467cf",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-02-12T09:45:00+00:00",
    "order": "2",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "text": "Promised savings never showed. Fuel and driver overtime ate the difference.",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2025-12-18T21:30:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467d0",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-02-12T09:45:00+00:00",
    "order": "3",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "text": "Find the board minutes where they voted to reverse.",
    "type": "to_do"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-01-09T13:20:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467d7",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-01T16:10:00+00:00",
    "order": "0",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "text": "Big Horn County. Kept the small schools open with shared staff instead of closing them. The middle path.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-01-09T13:20:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467d8",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-01T16:10:00+00:00",
    "order": "1",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "text": "The arrangement",
    "type": "heading_2"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-01-09T13:20:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467d9",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-01T16:10:00+00:00",
    "order": "2",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "text": "Shared a principal and specials teachers across two buildings. Doors stayed open, rides stayed short.",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-01-09T13:20:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467da",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-01T16:10:00+00:00",
    "order": "3",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "text": "Ask Gary whether Park County could share admin the same way.",
    "type": "to_do"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-01-15T10:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467e1",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T14:25:00+00:00",
    "order": "0",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f7",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f7",
    "text": "Board is seven seats. Need four to block consolidation. Updated after every call.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-01-15T10:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467e2",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T14:25:00+00:00",
    "order": "1",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f7",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f7",
    "text": "Where we stand",
    "type": "heading_2"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-01-15T10:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467e3",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T14:25:00+00:00",
    "order": "2",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f7",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f7",
    "text": "Solid no: me, Caldwell, Morrison. Leaning no: one. Yes: two. Undecided: one.",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-01-15T10:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467e4",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T14:25:00+00:00",
    "order": "3",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f7",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f7",
    "text": "Call the undecided seat before the November meeting.",
    "type": "to_do"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-02-03T18:50:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467eb",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T07:40:00+00:00",
    "order": "0",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f8",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f8",
    "text": "Keep it to three points. Bus time, cost, community. Don't get pulled into the weeds.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-02-03T18:50:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467ec",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T07:40:00+00:00",
    "order": "1",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f8",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f8",
    "text": "The three",
    "type": "heading_2"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-02-03T18:50:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467ed",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T07:40:00+00:00",
    "order": "2",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f8",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f8",
    "text": "45-minute rides for first-graders. No savings in four comparable counties. Close the school, you close the town.",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-02-03T18:50:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467ee",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T07:40:00+00:00",
    "order": "3",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f8",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f8",
    "text": "Tighten these to one page for the op-ed.",
    "type": "to_do"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-02-20T20:15:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467f5",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-01T22:30:00+00:00",
    "order": "0",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f9",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f9",
    "text": "Draft for the Enterprise. About 600 words. Lead with the bus, close with what these schools hold a town together.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-02-20T20:15:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467f6",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-01T22:30:00+00:00",
    "order": "1",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f9",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f9",
    "text": "Opening",
    "type": "heading_2"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-02-20T20:15:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467f7",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-01T22:30:00+00:00",
    "order": "2",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f9",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f9",
    "text": "A six-year-old shouldn't spend ninety minutes a day on a bus so a spreadsheet looks better.",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-02-20T20:15:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467f8",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-01T22:30:00+00:00",
    "order": "3",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f9",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f9",
    "text": "Send to Barbara for a read before I submit it.",
    "type": "to_do"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-03-12T09:30:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467ff",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T11:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "0",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "text": "Constituent meeting at Sage Creek. Reached 85 families across District 3. Good turnout for a weeknight.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-03-12T09:30:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185446800",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T11:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "1",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "text": "Takeaways",
    "type": "heading_2"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-03-12T09:30:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185446801",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T11:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "2",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "text": "Families want the case-study numbers in writing. Several offered to testify at the board meeting.",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-03-12T09:30:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185446802",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T11:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "3",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "text": "Send the four county summaries to everyone who signed in.",
    "type": "to_do"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-10-02T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854490a1",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T09:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "4",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "text": "By the numbers: enrollment fell from 96 to 79 in the three years after the 2014 closure. The district booked 120,000 dollars in projected annual savings; added bus fuel and two extra routes ran about 140,000 dollars a year, so the line went the wrong way.",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-10-02T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854490a2",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T09:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "4",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "text": "By the numbers: outlying one-way rides went from 25 to 48 minutes. Projected savings were 150,000 dollars a year; realized savings came in closer to 40,000 dollars once fuel and an added driver were paid.",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-10-02T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854490a3",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T09:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "4",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "text": "By the numbers: the district promised 180,000 dollars a year. Fuel ran an extra 95,000 dollars and driver overtime another 110,000 dollars, so the promised savings never showed. The board reversed the closure inside two years.",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-10-02T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854490a4",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T09:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "4",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "text": "By the numbers: sharing one principal and the specials staff across the two buildings saved about 115,000 dollars a year with both schools open and rides kept under 25 minutes.",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-10-02T11:05:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854490a5",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T11:05:00+00:00",
    "order": "4",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "text": "Five families offered to speak at the board session; they left their contact on the bus-route survey. Current enrollment: Sage Creek 92, Pronghorn Valley 78.",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item"
  }
